ass="no_margin">Torsten Sacher</h3><p>  <sup>4</sup> Max von Pettenkofer Institut f&#x000fc;r Virologie, Ludwig-Maximilians-Universit&#x000e4;t M&#x000fc;nchen, Munich, Germany </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Sacher%20T%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=17722980">Torsten Sacher</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm140672992827664"><h3 class="no_margin">Elena Tomasello</h3><p>  <sup>1</sup> Centre d\'Immunologie de Marseille-Luminy, Universit&#x000e9; de la M&#x000e9;diterran&#x000e9;e, Marseille, France </p><p>  <sup>2</sup> INSERM (U631), Marseille, France </p><p>  <sup>3</sup> CNRS (UMR6102), Marseille, France </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Tomasello%20E%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=17722980">Elena Tomasello</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm140672990204288"><h3 class="no_margin">Eric Vivier</h3><p>  <sup>1</sup> Centre d\'Immunologie de Marseille-Luminy, Universit&#x000e9; de la M&#x000e9;diterran&#x000e9;e, Marseille, France </p><p>  <sup>2</sup> INSERM (U631), Marseille, France </p><p>  <sup>3</sup> CNRS (UMR6102), Marseille, France </p><p>  <sup>5</sup> Assistance Publique-H&#x000f4;pitaux de Marseille and H&#x000f4;pital de la Conception, Marseille, France </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Vivier%20E%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=17722980">Eric Vivier</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm140672995979904"><h3 class="no_margin">Ulrich H Koszinowski</h3><p>  <sup>4</sup> Max von Pettenkofer Institut f&#x000fc;r Virologie, Ludwig-Maximilians-Universit&#x000e4;t M&#x000fc;nchen, Munich, Germany </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Koszinowski%20UH%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=17722980">Ulrich H Koszinowski</a></div></div><div id="_co_idm140672995204048"><h3 class="no_margin">Marc Dalod</h3><p>  <sup>1</sup> Centre d\'Immunologie de Marseille-Luminy, Universit&#x000e9; de la M&#x000e9;diterran&#x000e9;e, Marseille, France </p><p>  <sup>2</sup> INSERM (U631), Marseille, France </p><p>  <sup>3</sup> CNRS (UMR6102), Marseille, France </p><div>Find articles by <a href="/pubmed/?term=Dalod%20M%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=17722980">Marc Dalod</a></div></div></div></div><div class="contrib-group half_rhythm fm-editor">Bill Sugden, <span class="fm-role">Editor</span><sup></sup></div><div class="fm-panel half_rhythm"><div class="togglers"><a href="#" class="pmctoggle" rid="idm140672993072960_ai idm140673040463408_ai idm140672994794688_ai">Author information</a> <a href="#" class="pmctoggle" rid="idm140672993072960_an">Article notes</a> <a href="#" class="pmctoggle" rid="idm140672993072960_cpl">Copyright and License information</a> <a href="/pmc/about/disclaimer/">Disclaimer</a></div><div class="fm-authors-info fm-panel hide half_rhythm" id="idm140672993072960_ai" style="display:none"><div class="fm-affl" lang="en" id="aff1">  <sup>1</sup> Centre d\'Immunologie de Marseille-Luminy, Universit&#x000e9; de la M&#x000e9;diterran&#x000e9;e, Marseille, France </div><div class="fm-affl" lang="en" id="aff2">  <sup>2</sup> INSERM (U631), Marseille, France </div><div class="fm-affl" lang="en" id="aff3">  <sup>3</sup> CNRS (UMR6102), Marseille, France </div><div class="fm-affl" lang="en" id="aff4">  <sup>4</sup> Max von Pettenkofer Institut f&#x000fc;r Virologie, Ludwig-Maximilians-Universit&#x000e4;t M&#x000fc;nchen, Munich, Germany </div><div class="fm-affl" lang="en" id="aff5">  <sup>5</sup> Assistance Publique-H&#x000f4;pitaux de Marseille and H&#x000f4;pital de la Conception, Marseille, France </div><div class="fm-affl" lang="en" id="edit1">University of Wisconsin-Madison, United States of America</div><div id="cor1">&#x0002a; To whom correspondence should be addressed. E-mail: <a href="mailto:dev@null" data-email="rf.srm-vinu.lmic@dolad" class="oemail">rf.srm-vinu.lmic@dolad</a></div></div><div class="fm-article-notes fm-panel hide half_rhythm" id="idm140672993072960_an" style="display:none"><div class="fm-pubdate half_r